<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Running: Strength, Health, and Joy</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; /* Using Open Sans or falling back to sans-serif */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            /* Dynamic background image related to running, focusing on trails/nature */
            background: url('https://source.unsplash.com/1920x1080/?running,trail,marathon') no-repeat center center fixed;
            background-size: cover;
            color: #333; /* Dark grey for general text */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh; /* Ensures the page takes full viewport height */
            overflow-x: hidden; /* **Crucial for preventing horizontal scrolling** */
        }

        header {
            background: transparent; /* Completely transparent header */
            color: white; /* White text color */
            padding: 35px 0; /* More padding for a bolder header */
            text-align: center;
            position: relative; /* Allows z-index without being sticky */
            z-index: 1000;
        }

            header h1 {
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 4em; /* Even larger, prominent title */
                font-weight: 800; /* Extra bold */
                text-shadow: 3px 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); /* Stronger text shadow for readability */
                padding: 0 20px; /* Small padding to prevent text touching edges on small screens */
                letter-spacing: 1px; /* Subtle letter spacing */
            }

        /* Styles for each content section */
        .content-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); /* Slightly less transparent white background for sections */
            padding: 50px 0; /* More vertical padding for sections */
            margin-bottom: 25px; /* Spacing between sections */
            box-shadow: 0 6px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); /* Softer, wider shadow for each section */
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px); /* More pronounced "frosted glass" effect */
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px); /* For Safari */
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); /* Subtle top border */
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); /* Subtle bottom border */
            flex-shrink: 0; /* Prevents sections from shrinking */
        }

            /* Alternating background colors for sections */
            .content-section:nth-of-type(odd) {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92); /* White for odd sections */
            }

            .content-section:nth-of-type(even) {
                background: rgba(248, 255, 248, 0.92); /* Very light green tint for even sections */
            }

        /* Inner container for textual content within sections */
        .inner-content {
            max-width: 950px; /* Wider content area */
            margin: 0 auto; /* Centering inner content */
            padding: 0 40px; /* Horizontal padding within content */
        }

        h2 {
            color: #2e8b57; /* Sea Green - a fresh, natural color */
            margin-top: 0; /* No top margin to avoid duplicating with section padding */
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3cb371; /* Matching underline */
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 2.8em; /* Even larger headings */
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center; /* Centering headings */
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.9; /* More line spacing for readability */
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            font-size: 1.2em; /* Slightly larger text */
            text-align: justify; /* Justified text for a clean block look */
        }

        .benefits-list {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding-left: 0;
            margin-bottom: 40px; /* More spacing after the list */
        }

            .benefits-list li {
                background: #e6f7ed; /* Very light green background for list items */
                margin-bottom: 15px; /* More space between list items */
                padding: 18px 30px; /* More padding for list items */
                border-left: 7px solid #3cb371; /* Green accent bar */
                border-radius: 10px; /* More rounded corners */
                font-size: 1.15em;
                display: flex;
                align-items: flex-start; /* Align top of emoji with text */
                box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); /* Slightly stronger shadow for list items */
            }

                .benefits-list li::before {
                    content: '👟'; /* Running shoe emoji */
                    margin-right: 20px; /* More space after emoji */
                    font-size: 1.6em; /* Larger emoji */
                    flex-shrink: 0;
                    line-height: 1; /* Ensures emoji takes up less vertical space */
                    padding-top: 5px; /* Fine-tuning emoji alignment */
                }

                /* Adjusted styling for bold and non-bold text within list item to ensure alignment */
                .benefits-list li strong, .benefits-list li span {
                    vertical-align: top; /* Align both bold and non-bold parts to the top */
                    display: inline-block; /* Treat them as inline blocks to respect vertical-align */
                }


        .btn-club {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 40px auto 0 auto;
            background-color: #3cb371;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            text-decoration: none !important; /* **CRUCIAL: Ensure no underline** */
            border: none !important; /* **CRUCIAL: Ensure no border** */
            outline: none !important; /* **CRUCIAL: Remove outline on focus** */
            border-radius: 35px;
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer; /* Indicate it's clickable */
        }

            .btn-club:hover {
                background-color: #2e8b57;
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
            }

        footer {
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
            margin-top: auto;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        /* Responsive adjustments for smaller screens (IMPORTANT: @@media for Razor!) */
        @@media (max-width: 992px) {
            .inner-content {
                padding: 0 30px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1.1em;
            }

            .benefits-list li {
                font-size: 1.05em;
            }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 3em;
            }

            .content-section {
                padding: 40px 0;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .inner-content {
                padding: 0 25px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            p, .benefits-list li {
                font-size: 1em;
            }

            .btn-club {
                padding: 15px 35px;
                font-size: 1.2em;
            }
        }

        @@media (max-width: 480px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
                padding: 0 10px;
            }

            .content-section {
                padding: 30px 0;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
            }

            .inner-content {
                padding: 0 15px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.7em;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 0.95em;
            }

            .benefits-list li {
                font-size: 0.9em;
                padding: 15px 20px;
                flex-direction: column; /* Icon above text on small screens */
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

                .benefits-list li::before {
                    margin-right: 0;
                    margin-bottom: 8px; /* Space between icon and text */
                    font-size: 1.4em;
                    padding-top: 0; /* Reset padding-top for stacked layout */
                }

            .btn-club {
                width: 90%; /* Button takes 90% width on small screens */
                box-sizing: border-box; /* Padding included in width */
                font-size: 1.1em;
                padding: 15px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Running: Strength, Health, and Joy</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="content-section why-running">
        <div class="inner-content">
            <h2>Why Lace Up? The Incredible Benefits of Running</h2>
            <p>
                Running is more than just a physical activity; it's a journey towards better health and well-being.
                It's a fantastic way to improve cardiovascular health, strengthen your muscles and bones, and manage your weight.
                Beyond the physical, running offers significant mental benefits: it helps reduce stress, improves mood, and boosts self-confidence.
                It connects you with your surroundings and provides a sense of accomplishment with every step.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section key-facts">
        <div class="inner-content">
            <h2>Key Facts to Get You Moving</h2>
            <ul class="benefits-list">
                <li><strong>Boosts Cardiovascular Health:</strong> Running strengthens your heart and improves blood circulation.</li>
                <li><strong>Enhances Mental Well-being:</strong> It's a great way to relieve stress and boost mood.</li>
                <li><strong>Supports Weight Management:</strong> Running is an effective way to burn calories.</li>
                <li><strong>Increases Endurance:</strong> Regular running builds stamina and energy levels.</li>
                <li><strong>Strengthens Bones and Muscles:</strong> It contributes to overall physical strength.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="content-section call-to-action">
        <div class="inner-content">
            <h2>Ready to Join the Community?</h2>
            <p>
                Connect with other runners and explore local trails and events.
            </p>
            <a href="/Club" class="btn-club">Find Your Club</a>
        </div>
    </section>

   

</body>
</html>